name: RFKTR's Darkdream Diffusion v1.6 [OLD]
description:
IMPORTANT NOTE: This is old page. Darkdream Diffusion v1.6 is last version and it won't be updated any further. Further versions will come out under relaunched "RFKTR's Darkdream" name. For latest version go here: https://civitai.com/models/9119/rfktrs-darkdream

If you like my work and want to support me, you can donate on Ko-fi, It will be greatly appreciated.

You should only give credit if you believe that my efforts warrant recognition.

Otherwise just enjoy it!

modelVersions.name: v1.6
modelVersions.description:
Full release of 1.6

  • improvements to landscapes and number of other subjects

  • no VAE needed anymore

  • general cinematic FX improvements

  • widened knowledge base

  • face structures are further finetuned to my art

  • improved generation of bald bearded men

  • improved generation of gothic girls

  • improved generation of gothic lingerie

  • improved understanding of camera apertures

  • balanced saturation and overcooking

  • further balanced between style and realism

modelVersions.name: v1.5
modelVersions.description:
IMPORTANT: since i'm transitioning model from hyperrealistic to stylized hyperrealistic - it might generate overcooked and oversaturated images using 84k vae, so using of anythingv3 vae or any other anime vae is reccommended for now.

-retrained on 50% of concepts with better captioning.

-trained further, refined and broadened knowledge base.

-fixed several places where it lacked style.
-trained out large quantity of cartoon and classical painting styles.

-further pushed stylized hyperrealism.

-slightly increased influence of RFKTR's SineTempore.
